  <trk>
    <name>On the Sonnenweg to the viewpoint</name>
    <desc>Impressive hike through the unique mountain landscape of Hasliberg. Breathtaking panoramic view of Planplatten. Good mountain trail, somewhat long descent, but with a shortcut option.</desc>
